{
  "script_id": "three-body",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "夜空中的群星看似永恒不变，但它们其实都在引力的牵引下不停运动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "两个天体的运动，牛顿早已给出完美的椭圆轨道解答。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.74,
      "size": 43776,
      "text": "可一旦加入第三个天体，问题就变得出人意料地困难，这就是著名的三体问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "它困扰了数学家三百年，最终揭示了一个深刻的概念——混沌。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "gravity",
      "line_id": "grav-1",
      "filename": "gravity-grav-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/gravity-grav-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.39,
      "size": 22176,
      "text": "一切的根源是牛顿的万有引力定律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "gravity",
      "line_id": "grav-2",
      "filename": "gravity-grav-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/gravity-grav-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.89,
      "size": 46224,
      "text": "任意两个有质量的物体之间都存在引力，大小与质量成正比，与距离平方成反比。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "gravity",
      "line_id": "grav-3",
      "filename": "gravity-grav-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/gravity-grav-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.78,
      "size": 44496,
      "text": "每个天体都同时受到其他所有天体的引力，这些力叠加起来决定了它的加速度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "gravity",
      "line_id": "grav-4",
      "filename": "gravity-grav-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/gravity-grav-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.69,
      "size": 43056,
      "text": "我们用数值积分一小步一小步地推进，就能在计算机里重现这场引力之舞。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-1",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/chaos-chaos-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.52,
      "size": 40320,
      "text": "看这三颗星，它们相互追逐、缠绕，轨迹错综复杂，永不重复。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-2",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/chaos-chaos-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42336,
      "text": "三体问题没有一般的解析解，我们无法写出一个公式预测遥远未来的位置。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-3",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/chaos-chaos-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.83,
      "size": 45216,
      "text": "更惊人的是它对初值的敏感：起点哪怕只差千分之一，结局也会天差地别。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "chaos-4",
      "filename": "chaos-chaos-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/chaos-chaos-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "这就是蝴蝶效应，也是科幻小说《三体》里那个文明无法预测的根源。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "figure8",
      "line_id": "fig-1",
      "filename": "figure8-fig-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/figure8-fig-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "虽然大多数情况是混沌的，但人们也发现了极少数优雅的周期解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "figure8",
      "line_id": "fig-2",
      "filename": "figure8-fig-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/figure8-fig-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.79,
      "size": 44640,
      "text": "最美的就是这个 8 字解：三颗等质量的星，沿着同一条 8 字曲线永恒追逐。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "figure8",
      "line_id": "fig-3",
      "filename": "figure8-fig-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/figure8-fig-3.mp3",
      "duration": 3.14,
      "size": 50256,
      "text": "它在 1993 年才被发现，并在 2000 年被严格证明存在，是数学与天体力学的瑰宝。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.46,
      "size": 39312,
      "text": "现在你可以切换不同的初始构型，亲眼看看引力如何编排不同的舞蹈。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "试试混沌三体，再对比稳定的 8 字解，感受秩序与混沌的反差。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-3",
      "filename": "interaction-int-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "留意系统总能量这个数字，它在理想模拟中应当保持守恒。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "我们从万有引力出发，模拟了三体系统的运动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "我们见识了混沌、对初值的敏感，以及罕见而优雅的 8 字周期解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "three-body",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/three-body/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39744,
      "text": "简单的定律，无穷的复杂，宇宙的魅力正在于此。继续探索吧！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 51.24,
  "total_size": 819360
}